N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 358.9 - Record retention and disposition

State Regulations

Record retention and disposition of all records of the
county, any qualified manufacturer, and installation/service provider with
respect to this Part shall be in accordance with the applicable records
retention and disposition schedule promulgated by the State Education

Department. Notes
